<p>A collection of songs from the comic operas by <a href="/wiki/Author:W._S._Gilbert" class="mw-redirect" title="Author:W. S. Gilbert">W. S. Gilbert</a> and <a href="/wiki/Author:Arthur_Sullivan" class="mw-redirect" title="Author:Arthur Sullivan">Arthur Sullivan</a>.
</p>
