<div class="poem">
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r15431465" /><div class="wst-block-center" style="width:fit-content;"><br />
<p><span style="font-size:83%;">"Sleep on, ye pale civilians. <br />
<span class="wst-gap &#95;&#95;gap" style="display:inline-block; inline-size:2em"></span>All thunder-clouds defy, <br />
On Europe's countless millions <br />
<span class="wst-gap &#95;&#95;gap" style="display:inline-block; inline-size:2em"></span>The Sentry keeps his eye."</span><br />
</p>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r15431519" /><div class="wst-right">
<p><span style="font-size:92%;"><i>— Iolanthe</i></span>
</p>
</div><br />
</div>
</div>
<p><br />
